      "title": "Burnaby adopts new 25-year Official Community Plan (Burnaby 2050)",
      "summary": "The City of Burnaby has adopted a new Official Community Plan called Burnaby 2050, which replaces the 1998 plan. This long-term land use and policy framework will guide how the city grows, develops, and changes over the next 25 years. It covers housing, transportation, parks, climate action, and more. The new plan affects all future rezoning applications and development decisions in Burnaby.",
